f.edu/hyperNEATpage/HyperNEAT.html&quot;&gt;http://eplex.cs.ucf.edu/hyperNEATpage/H=
yperNEAT.html&lt;/a&gt;
into a place where people can have questions like yours a=
nswered. The
&quot;Introduction / What is HyperNEAT?&quot; section on that =
